data.description: Do you Want it all in your next home? Well this is the home for you... Unlike over 90% of the homes in our area, this home features an amazing basement, a true finish living space like an apartment.  Gorgeous 3 story home with finished basement! WOW what a treat! Features 9ft smooth ceilings, arched room openings, and dramatic entry. Kitchen lovers gourmet delight features granite countertops, 42 inch cabinets, center island, large pantry, and large eat in bar. Sunken GR w/ wood-burning marble fireplace. Formal DR w/ coffered ceiling and separate formal LR. The most amazing Hardwood Floors in Entry, Kitchen, and Breakfast Area. Double doors lead to massive owners suite featuring high tray ceiling, garden tub, separate shower, double sinks and over-sized closet in master bath. Large 1600 square footage finished walk out basement with two extra room a, one bath, flex room, and media room.  comfortable. Private fenced back yard w/ large deck and 50x12 patio. Seller will for you and only you, have the home painted on the interior, and the exterior trim, make sure your back patio is stunning and prepared for your family gathers. Dont miss this opportunity....you will not be disappointed.
